io.analytics.domain

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.analytics.domain.Account

  • public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an Account with our application. An Account is independent of a Google Account or a Google Analytics Account, this is specifically an Account with our application. An Account has few properties on its own, and is mostly defined by the relationships it has with other entities.
    Author:
    Dave Wong
